edu.kit.cm.kitcampusguide.standardtypes
Class MapSection

java.lang.Object
  edu.kit.cm.kitcampusguide.standardtypes.MapSection
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class MapSection
extends Object
implements Serializable

Represents a section of a map. Stores the northwest and southeast corner. Two MapSections representing the same section on a map (same north west and south east corner) don't need to be the same object, due to the WorldPositions coordinates being represented by doubles it's better to construct new MapSections if needed.

Author:
fred
